      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk it just feels like a pressure thing. i have some ear drops at home for wax, do u think i should just use those for a night and see if that clears the blockage and the pop sound? seems way easier than driving to a doctor for something that might just be a bit of wax or a pop.",
